name: Exploration | Special thank you
description:
This is a special thank you piece for all of you who have been supporting
and believing in my artworks. I've been surfing in NFT world for about one month. 

I never expected that i would go through this far. There always be ups and downs while building my personal branding on NFT thing; slow sales and unrecognized. But i always think of keep creating no matter how slow or fast it is being liked by others. Meeting new friends and new community then creating connection and seeing a bunch of cool artworks were most important thing and such amazing exploration! 

And here i am. Reaching this step for making a piece to thank you all.

So, this is it. A special piece "EXPLORATION". 

My journey has just begun.
